Farmers Insurance, the U.S. provider
of property-casualty coverage that has a management relationship
with  Zurich Insurance Group AG (ZURN) , hired Patrizio Spagnoletto as
head of digital strategy.  Spagnoletto was most recently vice president of global
marketing services for  Yahoo! Inc. (YHOO) , Los Angeles-based Farmers
said today in a statement distributed by PR Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
